."},"audio":{"fileName":""}},{"page":15,"title":"Snow White (최종)","graphic":{"name":"20.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"20.txt","data":"200E1127111D00193A011727110E00070A2711190A1D001E13110009151E1E011B11320000000000201E13113D0017111E25171D1119001E150000001E13110009151E1E011B11001E150000000000000A1D1E171519250911001E13110D0E110727110E1E1500200E1D153A00203A130A1E113200000000","plain":"Seven dwarves lived in the cottage. They returned to the cottage to introduce themselves to Snow White."},"audio":{"fileName":""}},{"page":14,"title":"Snow White (최종)","graphic":{"name":"21.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"21.txt","data":"200E1127111D0020193A011727110E0000000000","plain":"Seven Dwarves"},"audio":{"fileName":""}},{"page":13,"title":"Snow White (최종)","graphic":{"name":"22.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"22.txt","data":"200E1D153A00203A130A1E11000B11071E0000000E010B11003A0A1E13001E131100000000000000193A011727110E02000E15000E131100000000001911090A191119001E15000E1E013D003A0A1E131E13110D32000000000000000000000000000000","plain":"Snow White felt safe with the dwarves, so she decided to stay with them."},"audio":{"fileName":""}},{"page":12,"title":"Snow White (최종)","graphic":{"name":"23.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"23.txt","data":"201E131100201F2511111D000000000000000000190A0E09152711171119001E13011E001E13110013251D1E0E0D011D0013011900070A1119000000011D19001E13011E00200E1D153A000000000000203A130A1E11003A010E000E1E0A07070000000001070A2711320000000000000000000000000000","plain":"The Queen discovered that the huntsman had lied and that Snow White was still alive."},"audio":{"fileName":""}},{"page":11,"title":"Snow White (최종)","graphic":{"name":"24.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"24.txt","data":"200E1311000D0A2D11190001000F151E0A151D001E13011E000913011D1B111900131117000000000A1D1E1500011D001507190013011B0200011D190E1311000F150A0E151D111900011D0000000000010F0F0711001E15001B0A2711001E1500000000200E1D153A00203A130A1E113200000000000000","plain":"She mixed a potion that changed her i